<div id="block-block-3" class="block block-block even">

      
  <p>The Energy Biosciences Institute (EBI), largest public-private partnership of its kind in the world, was created in 2007 to address one of the 21st Century&rsquo;s greatest challenges &ndash; finding a technological solution to the problems associated with climate change, global warming, and the rising price and diminishing supplies of carbon-based fossil fuels.</p>
<br />
<br />
<p><a class="blue_button" href="content/energy-biosciences-institute">more</a></p>

</div><!-- /.block -->
